ick to be inserted into the mango; if the stick is not long enough you may not be able to remove the icy pole from moulds.","<strong>Creamy strawberry icy poles<\/strong>: Replace mango with 300 g frozen strawberries and proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","8h 15m","10 portions"]}